column2: SELECT TOP # sp.objID,  sp.ra,  sp.dec, px.plateID AS plateID, px.plate AS plate,  sp.mjd AS mjd, sp.fiberID AS fiberID, sp.z AS Z, sp.zErr AS Z_Err, sp.psfmag_u, sp.psfmag_g, sp.psfmag_r, sp.psfmag_i, sp.psfmag_z FROM specPhoto AS sp  JOIN plateX AS px ON (sp.plateID = px.plateID AND  sp.mjd = px.mjd) WHERE  (sp.class=&&&) AND zWarning = # AND ((sp.psfmag_u <= #) AND (sp.psfmag_u >#)) AND ((sp.psfmag_g <= #) AND (sp.psfmag_g >#)) AND ((sp.psfmag_r <= #) AND (sp.psfmag_r >#)) AND ((sp.psfmag_i <= #) AND (sp.psfmag_i >#)) AND ((sp.psfmag_z <= #) AND (sp.psfmag_z >#)) AND sp.dec > # - # ORDER BY Z
